Articles.Content: Without any of the overpowered mods get from kerbin to the mun from the mun to minmus and from minmus back to kerbin. Is that even possible? We\'ll see..
Can I do it the other way around? Kerbin to Minimus to Mun to Kerbin?
See [this topic](http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/index.php?topic=12346.0), as it already had this challenge. Also, people already completed this challenge.
